Feature: Hotel Booking in Adactin Application

Scenario: User Login In Web Application
Given user Launch In Adactin  Application
When user Enter The User Name In User Name Field
And  user Enter The Password In User Password Field
Then user click The Login Button And It Navigates To Search Hotel Page.

Scenario: User Search The Hotel in Search Hotel Page
When User Click The Location drop_down button And User Select the Location Field
And User Click The Hotel drop_down Button And User Select The Hotel Field
And User Click The Room Type drop_down Button And User Select The Room Type Field
And User Click The Number of Rooms drop_dowm Button And User Select The Number of Rooms Field
And User Enter The Check In Date Box In Check In Date Field
And User Enter The Check out Date Box In Check Out Date Field
And User Click The Adults Per Room drop_down Button And User select The Adults Field
And user Click The Children per Room drop_down Button And User Select The Children per Room
Then User Click The Search Button And It Navigates To Select Hotel Page

Scenario: User Can Able Select The Hotel in Select Hotel Page
When User Click The Select Radio Button In Select Field Click the Button
And User Click The Continue Button And It Navigates To Book  A Hotel Page

Scenario: User can Able To Confirm our details In Book A Hotel Page
When User Enter The First Name In First Name Field
And User Enter The Last Name In Last Name Field
And User Enter The Billing Addrss In Billing Address Field
And User Enter The Credit Card No In Credit Card No Field
And User Click The Credit Card Type drop_down Button And Credit Card Type Field
And USer Click The Select Months drop down button And User Select The Months Field
And User Click The Select Year drop down button And User Select The Year Field
And User Enter The CVV Number Box In CVV Number Field
Then User Click The Book Now And It Navigates To Booking Confirmation Page

Scenario: User Can be able To Check The Details In  Booking Confirmation Page
Then User Click The LogOut Button And It Navigates To Logout Processing Page

Scenario: User Can be Able see The Logout Page.
Then User Click the Login Again Button And It Naviagtes To LogIn Page

